## Next Steps (for deployment)

To view Speed Insights data in the Vercel dashboard:
1. Enable Speed Insights in your Vercel project dashboard (Project Settings → Speed Insights)
2. Deploy the application to Vercel
3. After deployment and user visits, metrics will appear in the Speed Insights dashboard

The code implementation is complete and production-ready.
